{
  "stem": "14190.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I fantasized a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I dreamed a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I wrote a little poetry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I wish I would have those.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I would show my nuns that were teaching me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I used to draw a lot and made-- just fantasized to have a lot of friends around me, people around me, you know, and make pictures of them, and give them names.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, and that's how-- I read a lot of poems of Mickiewicz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was beyond my years, but I so very-- I became so romantic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then when the time came, they started to-- to-- they were very outgoing when it comes to-- to education.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, very limited education and limited, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But in literature, for example, it was also very limited.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I did get a hold of this poetry book.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So they finally allowed me to keep it, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And a lot of things I didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I memorized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I remember still things by heart that I memorized then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and then when I was a little older, I started to sing in a choir.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But the choir was behind, like, a curtain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So people that were close could see me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That's how my mother, when she survived, she started to look for her kids, for her family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she walked literally from house to house to see if anybody, anybody would see us or know anything about us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And one woman told her that she doesn't know if, but she did see a young girl in the choir that resembles a little bit her description that what you are telling us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that's how she ended up coming to church.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't think-- that was probably the first time for my mother being in the church.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
